        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-wrench"></i> Challenges & Solutions</h2>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Technical Challenges</h3>
            <p>Integrating third-party biometric hardware with custom software while maintaining security standards and ensuring fast response times presented several challenges:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Hardware Integration:</strong> Worked with multiple biometric device SDKs to ensure compatibility across different fingerprint readers</li>
                <li><strong>Security Implementation:</strong> Implemented end-to-end encryption for biometric data transmission and storage</li>
                <li><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Optimized database queries and template matching algorithms to achieve sub-2-second response times</li>
                <li><strong>Error Recovery:</strong> Developed comprehensive error handling to gracefully manage device disconnections and reading failures</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Outcome & Impact</h2>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Project Results</h3>
            <p>Successfully implemented a secure authentication system that reduced login time by 60% while maintaining high security standards. The system has been deployed in production environment and has processed over 10,000 authentication requests with 99.9% accuracy rate. User feedback has been overwhelmingly positive, citing improved convenience and enhanced security as key benefits.</p>
        </div>
